<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{HeaderTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Nunito', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f7ff 0%, #faf8ff 100%); min-height: 100vh;">
    <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(112, 66, 148, 0.12);">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #704294 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #c5468e 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; position: relative;">
            <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; opacity: 0.1; font-size: 120px; line-height: 1;">üîê</div>
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; position: relative; z-index: 1;">{{HeaderTitle}}</h1>
            <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.95; position: relative; z-index: 1;">Secure Your Account Access</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div style="padding: 40px 30px; line-height: 1.8; color: #495057;">
            <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Hello,</p>

            <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px;">We received a request to reset the password for your account associated with <strong style="color: #704294;">{{UserEmail}}</strong>.</p>

            <!-- Security Alert -->
            <div style="margin: 25px 0; padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%); border: 1px solid #ffcc80; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; border-radius: 8px;">
                <div style="color: #e65100; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px;">‚ö†Ô∏è Security Alert</div>
                <div style="color: #bf360c; font-size: 14px;">If you did not request this password reset, please disregard this email and ensure your account is secure.</div>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 15px; margin: 25px 0 20px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">To reset your password, click the button below:</p>

            <!-- Reset Button -->
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{ResetLink}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 40px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #704294 0%, #8b5cf6 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(112, 66, 148, 0.3); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
                    Reset Password
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #adb5bd; margin-top: 15px; text-align: center;">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>

            <!-- Link Display -->
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #faf8ff 0%, #f5f3ff 100%); padding: 14px; border-radius: 8px; word-break: break-all; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px; margin: 15px 0; color: #704294; border-left: 3px solid #704294;">
                {{ResetLink}}
            </div>

            <!-- Expiry Notice -->
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce4ec 0%, #f8bbd0 100%); border: 1px solid #f48fb1; border-left: 4px solid #d63384; padding: 16px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #c2185b; font-weight: 700;">‚è∞ Time Sensitive</p>
                <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #880e4f;">This link will expire in <strong>{{ExpiryMinutes}} minutes</strong>. Please reset your password promptly.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Password Guidelines -->
            <h3 style="color: #704294; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Create a Strong Password</h3>

            <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #faf8ff 0%, #ffffff 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <ul style="padding-left: 25px; line-height: 2; color: #495057;">
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">Minimum 8 characters</strong> in length</li>
                    <li>Mix of <strong style="color: #704294;">uppercase</strong> and <strong style="color: #704294;">lowercase</strong> letters</li>
                    <li>Include <strong style="color: #704294;">numbers</strong> and <strong style="color: #704294;">special characters</strong></li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">Avoid reusing</strong> passwords from other accounts</li>
                    <li>Consider using a <strong style="color: #704294;">password manager</strong> for enhanced security</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #6c757d;">If you continue to experience issues accessing your account, our support team is ready to assist you.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 25px;">Best regards,<br><strong style="color: #704294;">TPMailer Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f7ff 0%, #faf8ff 100%); padding: 25px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">TPMailer</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd;">&copy; {{Year}} All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #c0c4cc;">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
